Sentencas: A precise, fast, and robust parameter extraction technique of solid oxide fuel cell models is extremely crucial for optimal control and behavior analysis.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, a novel extreme learning machine based method is proposed to extract unknown parameters of solid oxide fuel cell models including electrochemical model and simple electrochemical model.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At first, extreme learning machine is applied to overcome two thorny obstacles (e.g., data shortage and noised data) via predicting additional data and updating noised data.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Then, both original data collected from a 5 kW solid oxide fuel cell stack and processed data are transferred to effectively guide eight prominent meta-heuristic algorithms for effective parameter extraction.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The performance of extreme learning machine is thoroughly investigated in two typical operation conditions through a comprehensive comparison based on various training data.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Simulation results validate that the proposed approach can effectively contribute to searching efficient model parameters along with high accuracy, prominent stability, high speed, and great robustness.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Particularly, the accuracy of parameter extraction for electrochemical model and simple electrochemical model can be improved by 49.3% and 65.6% at most, respectively.
Titulo: Extreme learning machine based meta-heuristic algorithms for parameter extraction of solid oxide fuel cells
